{"title_page": "Limnephilus ornatus", "text_new": "{{Speciesbox\n| genus = Limnephilus\n| image = Caddisfly (Trichoptera) - Guelph, Ontario 2016-08-01 (01).jpg\n| species = ornatus\n| authority = Banks, 1897\n| display_parents = 2\n}}\n'''''Limnephilus ornatus''''' is a species of [[northern caddisfly]] in the family [[Limnephilidae]]. It is found in North America.<ref name=itis/><ref name=gbif/><ref name=buglink/><ref name=Morse2019/>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|refs=\n<ref name=itis>\n{{Cite web| title=''Limnephilus ornatus'' Report\n| url=https://www.itis.gov/servlet/SingleRpt/SingleRpt?search_topic=TSN&search_value=116094\n| website=Integrated Taxonomic Information System\n| accessdate=2019-09-24\n}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=gbif>\n{{Cite web| title=''Limnephilus ornatus''\n| url=https://www.gbif.org/species/1442577\n| website=GBIF\n| accessdate=2019-09-24\n}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=buglink>\n{{Cite web| title=''Limnephilus ornatus'' species Information\n| url=https://bugguide.net/node/view/40590\n| website=BugGuide.net\n| accessdate=2019-09-24\n}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=Morse2019>\n{{Cite web\n| accessdate = 2019-07-02\n| title = Trichoptera World Checklist\n| date = 2019\n| last1 = Morse | first1 = John C.\n| publisher = International Symposia on Trichoptera\n| url = https://entweb.sites.clemson.edu/database/trichopt/\n}}</ref>\n}}\n\n{{Taxonbar|from=Q1961784}}\n\n[[Category:Integripalpia]]\n[[Category:Articles created by Qbugbot]]\n[[Category:Insects described in 1897]]\n\n{{trichoptera-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Speciesbox\n| genus = Limnephilus\n| species = ornatus\n| authority = Banks, 1897\n| display_parents = 2\n}}\n'''''Limnephilus ornatus''''' is a species of [[northern caddisfly]] in the family [[Limnephilidae]]. It is found in North America.<ref name=itis/><ref name=gbif/><ref name=buglink/><ref name=Morse2019/>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|refs=\n<ref name=itis>\n{{Cite web| title=''Limnephilus ornatus'' Report\n| url=https://www.itis.gov/servlet/SingleRpt/Single